\v 1 Inkangala\x + 55.12. 35.6.\x* legwadule kuzajabula ngabo\x + 41.18. 53.2.\x*; lehlane ithokoze, ikhahlele njengerosi,
\v 2 ikhahlele kakhulu\x + 32.15.\x*, ithokoze langentokozo lokuhlabelela. Inkazimulo yeLebhanoni\x + 33.9.\x* izayinikwa, ubuhle beKharmeli\x + 33.9.\x*\x + Josh. 19.26.\x* leSharoni\x + 33.9.\x*\x + Josh. 12.18.\x*; khona kuzabona inkazimulo yeN\nd kosi\nd*, ubukhosi bukaNkulunkulu wethu.
