\v 3 Qinisani izandla ezibuthakathaka\x + Jobe 4.3,4. Heb. 12.12.\x*, liqinise amadolo axegayo.
\v 4 Tshonini kwabalenhliziyo ephangisayo \add lithi\add*: Qinani, lingesabi. Khangelani, uNkulunkulu wenu uzakuza ngempindiselo, uNkulunkulu \add el\add*omvuzo; yena uzakuza alisindise.
\v 5 Khona amehlo eziphofu ezavuleka\x + 29.18. 32.3. 42.7. Mat. 9.27-30. 11.5. 12.22. 20.30-34. 21.14. Joha. 9.6,7. Seb. 26.18. Hlab. 146.8.\x*, lezindlebe zezacuthe zivuleke\x + 29.18. 32.3. 42.7. Mat. 9.27-30. 11.5. 12.22. 20.30-34. 21.14. Joha. 9.6,7. Seb. 26.18. Hlab. 146.8.\x*\x + Mark. 7.32-35.\x*.
\v 6 Khona oqhulayo ezakweqa njengendluzele\x + Mat. 11.5. 15.30. 21.14. Joha. 5.3,8,9. Seb. 3.2-8. 8.7. 14.8-10.\x*, lolimi lwesimungulu luhlabelele\x + Mark. 7.32-35.\x*\x + 32.4. Mat. 9.32,33. 12.22.\x*; ngoba amanzi azaqhekeza endaweni elugwadule\x + 55.12. 35.6.\x*\x + 41.18. 43.19,20. 44.3,4. 48.21. Joha. 7.38,39. Isam. 22.17.\x*, lezifula enkangala.
