\v 8 Kuzakuba lomgwaqo omkhulu khona, lendlela\x + 30.21.\x*, ezathiwa yindlela yobungcwele; ongcolileyo\x + 52.1. Jow. 3.17. Hlab. 118.20. Heb. 12.14.\x* kayikudlula kuyo, kodwa izakuba ngeyalowo; abahambayo nga\add leyo\add*ndlela, loba beyizithutha, kabayikulahleka.
\v 9 Kakuyikuba khona isilwane lapho\x + 11.7-9. Levi 26.6.\x*, lesilo esiphangayo kasiyikwenyuka phezu kwayo, kasiyikutholwa lapho; kodwa abahlengiweyo\x + 51.10. 62.12.\x* bazahamba ngayo.
